title: What It's Like Being on Both Extremes
description:
With Tasia traveling this week, Camo sits down with us to talk about their weightloss journey. Camo reflects on the differences in how she's been treated by other's as her weight has fluctuated, how she's been slimming down, and why she thinks it's important to take care of your body.
For 50% off your first Care/of order, go to TakeCareOf.com and enter code “unfazed50”!
Go to GreenChef.com/unfazed130 and use code “unfazed130” to get $130 off plus free shipping!
